data.description: Welcome to 27648 Crooked Oak Lane. This Charming country farm house was  built in 1925 and is situated on a little over an acre.  This home has been almost completely renovated.   As you approach this home you will be drawn to the oversized wrap around front porch where you can relax and take in the tranquil setting.  Upon entering you will notice the beautiful hardwood floors, crown molding, winding staircase and open floorplan.  As you travel through the foyer you will be drawn to the family area which is open to the spacious   kitchen. The family room boasts an eye catching corner gas fireplace.  Off of the kitchen you will find a large utility room with front loading washer and dryer and ample storage You will find a full bathroom opposite the laundry room.  Upstairs you will discover 4 large bedrooms and a full bathroom. The detached two car garage has a large room upstairs that can be used as an office or studio. There is also a 4 stall barn on the property.  This is true country living.
